---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="What data we collect, how we use it, and your choices. We keep this minimal and plain." noindex={false}>
  <section class="section"><div class="container container-narrow prose flow">
    <Breadcrumbs crumbs={[{ label: 'Privacy' }]} />
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead">We keep data collection to a minimum and explain it plainly. This is a starting template — have it reviewed for your final legal wording.</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Anonymous analytics</strong> to understand which guides help people. We use privacy-friendly analytics and avoid intrusive tracking.</li>
      <li><strong>Your email</strong>, only if you choose to subscribe or download a guide. You can unsubscribe anytime.</li>
      <li><strong>Nothing from our calculators.</strong> The tools run entirely in your browser; the figures you enter are never sent to us.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies &amp; affiliate links</h2>
    <p>Some links are affiliate or referral links. A partner may set a cookie to credit a referral; this costs you nothing and never changes our recommendations.</p>

    <h2>Your choices &amp; rights</h2>
    <p>You can unsubscribe from emails at any time and request that we delete your details. To do so, contact us using the details on our <a href="/contact/">contact page</a>.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>We'll update this page as our setup evolves and note the date of significant changes.</p>
  </div></section>
</BaseLayout>
